1. Created a new directory in the alx-intermediate-frontend:
    mkdir -p alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss
    cd alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss

2. Install NVM (Node version manager)
    $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

3. Closed and reopened the bash terminal.
 
5. Installed Sass version 3.7.4
    npm install sass -v 3.7.4